Level 4
=======
* 1 Ability point
* 1d6 HP
* +1 BAB
* +1 Will
* +1 0th level spell
* +1 2nd-level spell
* Swap 1 spell
* +1 1st-level/day
* +3 2nd-level/day
* +4 skill ranks

Choices
-------
* Ability point in Charisma - raises to 18
* HP roll is 3.
* Extra cantrip, Message.
* Extra 2nd-level spell, Summon Monster 2.
* Spell swap Spark -> Mage Hand.
* Favoured class bonus goes to HP.
* Skill ranks:- Bluff, Knowledge(Undead), 2x Use Magic Device
